[WHY]
We want to add a visual confirm mode for DCC and MCache for
debugging purpose.

[HOW]
color pipes based on whether DCC is enabled and what MCache id
is used.
black - DCC disabled
red - DCC enabled
grey - 2 different MCaches used
other colors - 1 MCache used

